headline: Trump defends Saudi prince over journalist Khashoggi's murder
description: During the Saudi royal's visit to the White House – his first time in the US since the killing of Jamal Khashoggi in 2018 – Trump shielded him from journalists' questions. headline: London's 'mudlarks' scour the Thames for treasure
description: On the banks of the British capital's river, London's 'mudlarks' search for fragments of the past: ancient pottery, old coins, bone dice. These enthusiasts are less motivated by the value of the objects than by the stories they tell. Sometimes, their finds even end up in a museum, as is currently being shown in an exhibition at the London Museum.
